Module com.example.bankingtransactionsgui
Package com.example.bank

Class AccountDatabase

java.lang.Object
com.example.bank.AccountDatabase
public class AccountDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
Keeps track of all the accounts in the bank. Contains an array of all the accounts at the bank and the number of accounts there are. Implements different methods to manipulate the accounts array depending on actions taken by clients.
Author:
Akshat Mehta and Atharva Patil
